ItemDescription: Biodiversity: Intensive plots where full species list has been verified.
Classification: Complete list of species but generally without vouchers and likely missing uncommon non-vasculars
Support: Species list complete enough for accurate assessment of site units but not complete enough for use in site unit development
Insufficient: Plots missing key information that maybe retrievable
Poor quality: Major species not identified, very limited species lists etc.
Visuals: Limited data but georeferenced site unit calls. Should be removed from BECMaster to a locations dataset
Remove: Plots are substandard and of limited value
